title: Your Wings Are Coming | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Your Wings Are Coming | Joel Osteen
description:
A caterpillar becomes a butterfly through a period of concealment. In the same way, God uses seasons of obscurity to transform us.

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
